Program: The History Hour
Title: Michael Jackson's Thriller
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03b1t0s
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 28 Dec 2015
The 1982 release of the world's best selling album; plus the untimely death of General George S Patton; the former child star Karolyn Grimes on the film It's A Wonderful Life, the Beagle 2 mission to Mars, and Vladimir Nabokov's scandalous book, Lolita. (Photo: Michael Jackson and assorted zombies in the video for Thriller in 1983. Credit: 01/01/1983 Publicity Handout) Show less